Definition: perennial of coastal sands and shingles of northern Europe and Baltic and Black Seas having racemes of small white flowers and large fleshy blue-green leaves often used as potherbs
Synonyms: sea_cole, Crambe_maritima, herb, genus_Crambe, m, perennial, of, coastal, sands, and, shingles, northern, Europe, Baltic, Black, Seas, having, racemes, small, white, flowers, large, fleshy, blue-green, leaves, often, used, as, potherbs
Category: noun.plant
